<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-5552-2/Hyper_Wormhole.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="Hyper_Wormhole.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
